==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Selection
<hw>Se*lec"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>selectio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>s⟦eacute⟧lection</ets>.]</ety> .
<def>The act of selecting, or the state of being selected; choice, by
preference.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is selected; a collection of things
chosen; <as>as, a choice <ex>selection</ex> of books</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Natural selection</b></col>. <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <cd>See
under <er>Natural</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Selective</ent>⟦br⟧
